					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">A couple of ways.  The Western SMS BIOS does a checksum of a cartridge, while the JP SMS doesn't.<br /><br />Also, the joystick port's data/direction lines are handled differently between the regions, making some of the peripherals incompatible too.</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://www.chrismcovell.com">http://www.chrismcovell.com</a><!-- m --></div>
